-- First Quantum Extends Its Hostile Offer for Inmet to Feb. 27
-- B y   S i m o n   C a s e y
-- 2013-02-08T16:14:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-08/first-quantum-extends-its-hostile-offer-for-inmet-to-feb-27.html
First Quantum Minerals Ltd. extended
its hostile C$5.1 billion ($5.1 billion) bid for Inmet Mining
Corp. to 5 p.m. New York time on Feb. 27 to give it more time to
get the necessary regulatory approvals.  First Quantum, which is based in Vancouver, commented today
in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
